Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不去上学 就在这懒懒散散无所事事浑浑噩噩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死啦! 我自己能收拾 你出去啦! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啦是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波说今晚要开个誓师大会 你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 总之先在车站前面等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 鹤见你是根本没吃够苦头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副「只有自己才了解松雪同学」的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高181厘米 体重68公斤 喜欢吃的东西是八桥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:58.15,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八桥（八ツ橋）：京都代表性的名点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱好是女装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女装?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等! 鹤见 话还没说完…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想把那事传得尽人皆知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见…? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 动起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是为芽间明天成佛而设的大宴会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好地装点一下! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间用纸巾来做花～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你可是宴会的主角啊 为什么还自己动手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很好玩嘛! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢! 芽间很行嘛! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 别发呆了 快用传单做垃圾箱 垃圾箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾箱? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前啊 我在班上不是很没用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠做傻事引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仁碳你们却让我成为了大家的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然…到头来…也只能看着大家而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能看着…而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次啊 全部都让我一个人操办好了! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会气气派派地送你走的哦 芽间! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}波波真是体贴呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个事情 打算怎么办? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把人愚弄到什么地步他们才满意? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群小孩 到底要到什么地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 小聪? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 冷静点! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈啊 你知道我身高多少吗? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一年来 我可是长高了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很孤单吧 你 还有聪志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能忘记掉芽衣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起分担孤单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 和聪志 还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起分担…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成什么样子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说 如果把烟花放上去了? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说如果芽间不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也想过好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得如果芽间不在了 跟仁碳最要好的就会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当芽间真的不在了 跟仁碳的距离却拉得远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然 距离又开始缩短了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是因为芽间回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去秘密基地吗? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟安城在一起? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…? 嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孬种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹤见子? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你那么信誓旦旦地说要让她成佛 到了关键时刻又怕了? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为害怕 所以逃离了芽间而跟安城在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是希望悲惨的不仅仅是你自己吧? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间在电话里叫我们出来的时候 她说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「为了仁碳 我有事情想拜托你们」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 雪集? 鹤见子说了什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这是只有你才能做的事情 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙 为啥不来啊! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.18,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,120)}{\c&H3842BB&}再{\c&H538BEC&}见{\c&H4FFFF0&}了 {\c&H51B25B&}芽{\c&HA07E37&}间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦 反正明天也会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫他们! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 喂 波波! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买了些点心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦! 不愧是鹤见子! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:52.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哦哦! 爱死你了 雪集! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇! 开party啦! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:57.12,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Party party…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信的! 我真的是相信你们的! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心死我了 真的! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦! 我爱死这个了! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}居然到齐了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…一切就要迎来结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 芽间和我们 组成了「超和平Busters」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开场白就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请主角芽间 上前来! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(403,146)}今天为了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(924,170)}芽间前来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(399,416)}谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是…
